This area is called the green zone. We call it the green zone because it's very green to your eyes, which is freshening. It's the spot where we often have physical activities or even do our school tasks. I think this is the most comfortable spot in our school. Fresh air is provided here and in the morning you can feel the swirling wind. It makes our school look beautiful. But it would be better if we have some benches to sit on in this area because to a lot of students, this is the perfect place to think and search for ideas.  The stone paths should be repaired too because some of them are broken. It will make the green zone looks way better and it will make a great photo spot. #XIMIPA4
